descriptionHtml:
Hello everyone i hope you found it useful this modders resources for your mods
I made this modders resources by request
==================================================================================================================================
About modders resources :

- This modders resources is made using NifSkope,Paint.net and vanilla meshes & textures
- This modders resources only included Wine,Orange Juice,SilverCup textures and modified vanilla meshes
- Other textures is not included because come from main game
==================================================================================================================================
Change log :

- Version 1.1 Updated version with slightly translicent and darker wine textures by Galadreal . Please see Screenshots.
- Version 1.2 fixed meshes minor issues
- Version 1.3 add WineGoldenGoblet
- Version 1.4 add OrangeJuiceGoldenGoblet
- Version 1.5 add : OrangeJuiceSilverCup01,SilverCup01,WineSilverCup01
==================================================================================================================================
